  "description": "pi-mcp is a Pi coding agent extension that allows connecting to MCP (Model Context Protocol) HTTP servers. It auto-discovers tools from MCP servers and registers them as native Pi tools. Features: Connect to MCP servers via Streamable HTTP or SSE, Auto-discover and register MCP tools, Global and per-project server configurations",
